modules.description: This module maps file extensions to MIME types and vice versa using predefined rules. It operates on strings representing filenames or MIME types, returning corresponding MIME types or file extensions. Use it to determine the MIME type of a file based on its extension or find file extensions associated with a specific MIME type.

This module maps file extensions and filenames to MIME types based on RFC2045 standards, using internal data to perform lookups. It supports converting extensions to MIME types, filenames to MIME types, and MIME types back to lists of extensions. Use it when handling HTTP content types, file uploads, or email attachments where accurate MIME type detection is required.
